extends layout

block main
  div.dilute-background
    h1 Greetings hooman!
    if !(userNames.firstname||userNames.lastname)
      div
        a(href="/account") It looks like you have an incomplete profile, would you like to complete that now? It would facilitate an enhancement of my salutations.
    if !existsContact
      div 
        a(href="/contacts") You don't currently have any contacts, would you like to create some?
    if connectionsEmpty
      h2 Congratulations, you have met your connection objectives for this week
      h3 If you feel unsatisfied with your connections interface this week...
